cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on improving the representation capacity of the network for action recognition, which is a task related to computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new approach to improve the last layers of the network, which involves machine learning (LG) and neural networks (NE). Additionally, the paper mentions exploiting recent advances in fine-grained recognition literature, which is related to multimedia (MM) and artificial intelligence (AI).
